tags.description: A legacy of the former Lake Grove School District, this park is open only to local residents who obtain a permit each year. Paid for by local property tax, permits and admissions are free to all Lake Grove Park District residents.
tags.name: Lake Grove Swim Park
tags.note: 2025 open dates were from June 14 to August 24. The office is only staffed during the season. To be updated when the 2026 open dates are announced.
tags.operator: Lake Oswego School District for Lake Grove Park District
